 you live each day as it was your last, someday you’ll most certainly be right.","location":"Kapaau","rating":5,"lat":20.230451,"lng":-155.801279,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"c287599f-2019-46d3-81a7-80ebcd0a2d88","name":"Craig Cain - Kiso Method","image":"","type":"practitioner","modality":"Chiropractic, Acupuncture, Massage, Alternative Therapy","modalities":["Chiropractic","Acupuncture","Massage","Alternative Therapy"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Find relief and healing at Awakening Healing Center in Hilo, Hawai'i. We offer chiropractic care, massage therapy, acupuncture, Vax-D, physical therapy, and veterans' services, all using the unique Kiso Method. Schedule your appointment today!","location":"Hilo","rating":5,"lat":19.726014,"lng":-155.088223,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"b41b7d7e-a6af-4971-b1f1-71944c482f64","name":"Eric Mizuba","businessName":"The 02 Lab Hawaii & Mizuba Chiropractic","image":"https://cdcssl.ibsrv.net/ibimg/smb/300x300_80/webmgr/08/h/4/chiromatrix_chiropractic_og.jpg.webp?37502cfa0df7b63c44180df77de0892f","type":"practitioner","modality":"Alternative Therapy, Chiropractic","modalities":["Alternative Therapy","Chiropractic"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Home in Kamuela, HI. Mizuba Chiropractic is your local Chiropractor in Kamuela serving all of your needs. Call us today at 808-491-2462 for an appointment.","location":"Waimea","rating":5,"lat":20.020506,"lng":-155.669731,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"82dd66c7-ec51-409b-993d-6612b6e06a91","name":"Well Wahine","businessName":"Well Wahine","image":"http://static1.squarespace.com/static/58a14697a5790a7c3fc8db63/t/58a278d5ff7c5033d602abb