o health consultations and whole food detoxes, Kelli utilizes all to help strengthen the relationship one has with their individual self.","location":"Holualoa","rating":5,"lat":19.619523,"lng":-155.948696,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"572f47aa-0eb0-45ef-b430-0153b5a2fe6d","name":"Hawaii Center for Regenerative Medicine: Liza R Maniquis-Smigel","businessName":"Hawaii Center for Regenerative Medicine","image":"http://static1.squarespace.com/static/62e2d30e1c2c88233afed9a7/t/673d8ae27cea230f472f9b31/1732086498677/Regen+Hawai%E2%80%99i+%28500+x+100+px%29+%283%29.png?format=1500w","type":"practitioner","modality":"Alternative Therapy, Longevity, IV Therapy","modalities":["Alternative Therapy","Longevity","IV Therapy"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"","location":"Hilo","rating":5,"lat":19.723498,"lng":-155.089748,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"a200060b-44a3-4d34-9818-0b0d3a0f0f64","name":"Integrative Healthcare","businessName":"Ho'o Lokahi Health","image":"https://sccksxvjckllxlvyuotv.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/practitioner-images/avatars/1772150080706_ymsn9s7sqp.webp","type":"practitioner","modality":"Alternative Therapy, Naturopathic","modalities":["Alternative Therapy","Naturopathic"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Integrative healthcare specialists to support health naturally located in Hawaii","location":"Kailua Kona","rating":5,"lat":19.686898,"lng":-156.015737,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"e6b9190b-3712-4822-a948-eb68658ff6f7","name":"Upcoming Offerings","businessName":"Wild Women Hawai'i LLC","image":"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/4bf6fb_269e2ecdc5a04812a4d3df12517ffe82~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_1108,h_732,al_c/4bf6fb_269e2ecdc5a04812a4d3df12517ffe82~mv2.png","type":"practitioner","modality":"Alternative Therapy, Somatic Therapy, Women's Health, Nature Therapy","modalities":["Alternative Therapy","Somatic Therapy","Women's Health","Nature Therapy"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Women’s retreats, somatic therapy, and women’s gatherings in Hilo and across the Big Island. Wild Women Hawai'i hosts private women’s gatherings rooted in wellness and friendship.","location":"Hilo","rating":5,"lat":0,"lng":0,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"4f0201fe-fd88-4166-860b-5f2e3eff5106","name":"Michelle Wellman","businessName":"Woman Of Horses","image":"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/754508_5959ad9afad5470f87d98a3218aef380%7Emv2_d_2300_1534_s_2.jpg/v1/fit/w_2500,h_1330,al_c/754508_5959ad9afad5470f87d98a3218aef380%7Emv2_d_2300_1534_s_2.jpg","type":"practitioner","modality":"Alternative Therapy, Nature Therapy","modalities":["Alternative Therapy","Nature Therapy"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"\nEquine Assisted Therapy\n\nEAGALA certified and ready to offer equine assisted psychotherapy! The team approach of a Mental Health Professional, Equine Specialist and Equine herd sets the space for transitions to happen in those seeking therapy. This is a post modern method and is 100% on the ground. With my team we can offer solution oriented sessions to hold space for you to heal. Contact for more information or to schedule a session.","location":"Waikoloa","rating":5,"lat":19.927062,"lng":-155.783519,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"b393f147-f777-4b4a-a091-74aa35e44fe7","name":"Robbi Nanni","businessName":"Waikōloa Stables","image":"https://www.waikoloa.org/editor_upload/Image/Waiko%CC%84loaVillageAssociation.jpg","type":"practitioner","modality":"Alternative Therapy, Nature Therapy","modalities":["Alternative Therapy","Nature Therapy"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Therapeutic Horse Riding\n\nRobbi Nanni is a Professional Association of Therapeutic Horsemanship (PATH) certified riding instructor who provides riding lessons to students with cognitive and/or physical disabilities.  Horses are extremely therapeutic and can help individuals overcome anxiety, learn to walk, talk, and many other breakthroughs for the student.  Depending on the student’s level of riding or disability there are two volunteers in addition to the instructor per rider during the lesson.","location":"Waikoloa","rating":5,"lat":19.927199,"lng":-155.782814,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"908d8648-0780-4d7c-9951-e9666e72e954","name":"Hawaii Kailua Kona Therapist","image":"http://nebula.wsimg.com/a69c486667e7ed0f9e16a849b300d06e?AccessKeyId=896F41EBC3B7F3A125B6&disposition=0&alloworigin=1","type":"practitioner","modality":"Psychotherapy, Alternative Therapy","modalities":["Psychotherapy","Alternative Therapy"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Relief from Toxic Thoughts and Sabotaging Memories. Video and description of Summer Eggleston MFT, CSAC - her tools, methods and techniques, featuring Thought Field Therapy.","location":"Kona","rating":5,"lat":19.626512,"lng":-155.986455,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"2d201710-8442-4744-a160-58ecea325d33","name":"Vivienne W. Aronowitz","image":"","type":"practitioner","modality":"Alternative Therapy, Nutrition","modalities":["Alternative Therapy","Nutrition"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"","location":"Waimea","rating":5,"lat":20.023839,"lng":-155.676477,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"cae0b726-5fa4-4376-8ada-915f691b052c","name":"Wellness All Ways ","image":"//via.placeholder.com/1","type":"practitioner","modality":"Acupuncture, Alternative Therapy, Women's Health","modalities":["Acupuncture","Alternative Therapy","Women's Health"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"At Wellness All Ways we offer Acupuncture and integrative medicine. You will discover holistic healing at the root cause. We specialize in women's health, fertility, pain, digestion & more. We provide a healing sanctuary coupled with support and guidance to help you achieve your healing goals.","location":"Kona","rating":5,"lat":19.607113,"lng":-154.968067,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false}],"centers":[{"id":"70f5dab8-f665-4a3c-96df-2d964b490d39","name":"Advanced Wellness and Recovery","image":"https://www.advancedhawaii.com/","modality":"Functional Medicine, Alternative Therapy, Longevity","modalities":["Functional Medicine","Alternative Therapy","Longevity"],"location":"Kailua-Kona","rating":5,"lat":19.64494,"lng":-155.992732,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"At Advanced Wellness and Recovery in Kailua-Kona, we use Integrative Medicine in Hawaii. Reverse the signs of aging and restore mental health. Contact us today!","centerType":"wellness_center","centerTypeLabel":"Wellness Center","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"5dd9c8ab-4bd5-4a57-a5a5-1577236955bf","name":"ALO+HA","image":"https://aloandha.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/ClinicEntrance-scaled.jpg","modality":"IV Therapy, Longevity, Alternative Therapy","modalities":["IV Therapy","Longevity","Alternative Therapy"],"location":"Waimea","rating":5,"lat":20.022645,"lng":-155.675375,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"WaimeaÊ