ls who specialize in both traditional and alternative therapies, including naturopathic and holistic medicine. The dedicated team focuses on healing the body by identifying the root cause of illness, instead of focusing on the disease or symptoms.\n\nIn addition to managing your primary medical needs, the team at Kona Health & Aesthetics specializes in intravenous therapy, peptide therapy, and weight loss protocols. To improve your overall health and well-being, patients also have access to nutrition guidance and hormone therapy. ","centerType":"wellness_center","centerTypeLabel":"Wellness Center","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"1eb45745-b027-47c7-b0cc-4ab08089daf7","name":"Kona Quantum Vitality","image":"","modality":"Longevity, Alternative Therapy","modalities":["Longevity","Alternative Therapy"],"location":"Kailua-Kona","rating":5,"lat":19.642939,"lng":-155.99365,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"Kona Quantum Vitality has a growing team of individuals passionate about the healing and awakening of humanity.    Each person on the team has their unique story of overcoming darkness, finding healing, and developing a burning desire to help others.","centerType":"wellness_center","centerTypeLabel":"Wellness Center","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"451bf2a1-2c15-4735-b373-e75ddc2eda23","name":"Kualoli Retreats","image":"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/671131_3e4291ba9ad443818c56cf54f7f18404%7Emv2.jpg/v1/fit/w_2500,h_1330,al_c/671131_3e4291ba9ad443818c56cf54f7f18404%7Emv2.jpg","modality":"Alternative Therapy, Yoga","modalities":["Alternative Therapy","Yoga"],"location":"Pahoa","rating":5,"lat":19.410709,"lng":-154.902195,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"Private retreats on Hawai‘i’s wild and raw Puna Coast, Big Island. Kūa