wing a unique interaction.  It is very important that you are treated with the utmost compassion and understanding, for it is  your  body and your time to heal.","centerType":"clinic","centerTypeLabel":"Clinic","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":["http://static1.squarespace.com/static/69688813fd596d59577d633c/t/69782e2a8ab4f94f3bdbd3bb/1769483818129/Makai+Logo+2026.png?format=1500w"],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"c9f5d884-d1c8-434a-ba8e-6faaf67b2ae0","name":"Malama Chiropractic Clinic","image":"https://www.malamachiropractic.com/wp-content/uploads/bb-plugin/cache/Chiropractor-Kailua-Kona-HI-Jesse-Broderson-circle.jpg","modality":"Acupuncture, Alternative Therapy, Chiropractic, Massage, Naturopathic, Osteopathic","modalities":["Acupuncture","Alternative Therapy","Chiropractic","Massage","Naturopathic","Osteopathic"],"location":"Kailua-Kona","rating":5,"lat":19.643419,"lng":-155.996542,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"Are you looking for acupuncture in Kailua-Kona? Call the team at Malama Chiropractic Clinic today for help.","centerType":"wellness_center","centerTypeLabel":"Wellness Center","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{"fri":null,"mon":null,"sat":null,"sun":null,"thu":null,"tue":null,"wed":null},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"00d50832-b8bd-4943-9442-1f7e57767718","name":"Malama I Ke Ola","image":"http://static1.squarespace.com/static/6214458339aeb966faec2548/t/643ca5a86057841b610498d9/1681696168383/Malama+i+ka+Olaa-Logo-01.png?format=1500w","modality":"Alternative Therapy, Naturopathic, Sound Healing, Yoga","modalities":["Alternative Therapy","Naturopathic","Sound Healing","Yoga"],"location":"Holualoa","rating":5,"lat":19.619734,"lng":-155.949247,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"At Malama i ke Ola, we believe that true wellness, balance and harmony come from addressing the whole person, mind, body, and spirit. Our team of highly skilled and intuitive expert practitioners is committed to providing  you  an enriching experience and we are deeply honored to be a part of your healing journey.","centerType":"wellness_center","centerTypeLabel":"Wellness Center","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"90807bd5-e6fc-495a-8182-6d9939a0e718","name":"Malama Pono Massage","image":"http://static1.squarespace.com/static/6546b5b41b260d0b9aec73d6/t/698f9b8cf0ec637b7aa04fb9/1771019148388/MalamaPono-Logo_B%26W.png?format=1500w","modality":"Alternative Therapy, Massage, Naturopathic","modalities":["Alternative Therapy","Massage","Naturopathic"],"location":"Kailua-Kona","rating":5,"lat":19.64,"lng":-155.9969,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"Known as the Best Kona Massage in reviews: \"Not just the best massage on the island, probably the best massage in the world!\"","centerType":"wellness_center","centerTypeLabel":"Wellness Center","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"9013c4e1-0fa8-4c5e-80d4-62f41c0037a9","name":"Mana Wellness Massage Therapy & Holistic Health","image":"https://sccksxvjckllxlvyuotv.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/practitioner-images/729961b9d1321704102c925635d327f6.jpg","modality":"Alternative Therapy, Counseling, Herbalism, Lomilomi / Hawaiian Healing, Massage, Naturopathic, Network Chiropractic, Osteopathic","modalities":["Alternative Therapy","Counseling","Herbalism","Lomilomi / Hawaiian Healing","Massage","Naturopathic","Network Chiropractic","Osteopathic"],"location":"Hilo","rating":5,"lat":19.724544,"lng":-155.08623,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"Nestled in downtown Hilo, Hawaii on the Big Island, Mana Wellness Massage Therapy & Holistic Health provides professional massage therapy at our convienient location at 224 Kamehameha Ave Ste 206 Hilo, HI 96720. Wehope you give yourself the opprotunity for some massage & relaxation at our small Spa.","centerType":"wellness_center","centerTypeLabel":"Wellness Center","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"28e7f4f1-2caf-4766-bc78-4cfef8c90e6e","name":"Muaisa Hale Pule","image":"https://sccksxvjckllxlvyuotv.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/practitioner-images/centers/1774581196622-4yd8ujey4tx.webp","modality":"Energy Healing, Counseling, Meditation, Alternative Therapy, Soul Guidance, Art Therapy, Nature Therapy","modalities":["Energy Healing","Counseling","Meditation","Alternative Therapy","Soul Guidance","Art Therapy","Nature Therapy"],"location":"Captain Cook","rating":5,"lat":19.518149,"lng":-155.920678,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"Muaisa Hale Pule's principal aim is its spiritually-focused programs, sessions and retreats. Whether you're kama'aima (an island resident) or you're visiting from off-island, we offer donor-funded guidance, direction, retreats, vision quests, and natural healing venues to support inner needs and assist with spiritual housekeeping.\n\n* * * * * 5.0\n\"My husband and i got all we needed and more. ZZ and Jack are absolutely the BEST. Their expertise spans far greater than you can imagine.\" \n--DM, 2022","centerType":"retreat_center","centerTypeLabel":"Retreat Center","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":["https://sccksxvjckllxlvyuotv.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/practitioner-images/centers/1774581196622-4yd8ujey4tx.webp"],"workingHours":{"fri":null,"mon":null,"sat":null,"sun":null,"thu":null,"tue":null,"wed":null},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"5ed582a9-7c48-4f57-b0a0-c3b0754d7981","name":"Naluhia Floatation Therapy","image":"https://www.naluhiafloats.com/uploads/1/0/8/4/108418989/published/qigong-exerc