{"id":"17c2366f-f61b-4af9-872c-d1b27cc89639","name":"Pacific Quest","image":"https://pacificquest.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/PQ-website-logo-reverse-4e50f52f51a1d6b571b9f1ab11556430.png","modality":"Alternative Therapy, Counseling, Functional Medicine, Nutrition","modalities":["Alternative Therapy","Counseling","Functional Medicine","Nutrition"],"location":"Hilo","rating":5,"lat":19.725815,"lng":-155.060092,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"Pacific Quest provides fully licensed and accredited residential mental healthcare on the Island of Hawaii. Our integrative, individualized approach combines specialized clinical care, nature-based experiences and holistic wellness to boost self-esteem, heal trauma, and get to the root cause of what might be holding residents back.","centerType":"clinic","centerTypeLabel":"Clinic","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"b824f81e-5eab-46a5-b8a5-09f9327472d8","name":"Pilates of Hawaii","image":"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6518e8e5b205e37e6db4dd2b/282d61a0-9cf6-4c04-aae9-8f9fc23019b8/IMG_0205.png","modality":"Alternative Therapy, Ayurveda, Massage, Nutrition, Physical Therapy, Somatic Therapy, Yoga","modalities":["Alternative Therapy","Ayurveda","Massage","Nutrition","Physical Therapy","Somatic Therapy","Yoga"],"location":"Waimea","rating":5,"lat":20.022645,"lng":-155.675375,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"Cynthia is so grateful to be able to lead and teach such a spectacular form of movement therapy! She is continuously enriched by those that she has encountered within the Pilates studio, as teaching is one of the greatest gifts there are as it guides, nurtures and cultivates one's life journey.","centerType":"yoga_studio","centerTypeLabel":"Yoga Studio","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":["https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6518e8